Billionaire System PWA Money Tracker with Motivational Engine
💰 Billionaire System
A lightweight, installable PWA for tracking your wealth journey from R0 to R1M — with built-in motivation, daily earnings logging, and focus alerts.
🚀 What It Does
Table
Feature	Description
🔥 Motivation Engine	Auto-generates hustle quotes every 4 hours to keep your mindset locked in
📊 Daily Money Tracker	Log earnings in real-time with persistent localStorage
🎯 R0 → R1M Goal Bar	Visual progress tracker showing exactly how close you are to your first million
🔔 Focus Notifications	Browser push alerts with motivational reminders — even when the app is closed
📱 Installable PWA	Works offline, no app store needed — add to home screen on mobile or desktop
🛠 Tech Stack
Pure HTML5 + CSS3 + Vanilla JavaScript — zero dependencies
Service Worker for offline PWA support
Web Notifications API for push reminders
localStorage for persistent data
📦 Quick Start
Clone or download the repo
Open index.html in any modern browser
Click "Enable Alerts" to activate notifications
Start tracking. Start grinding.
🎯 Perfect For
Entrepreneurs tracking daily revenue
Side-hustlers building toward their first million
Anyone who wants a no-BS financial accountability tool
⚡ Install It
Because it's a PWA, you can install it directly to your device — no app store required.
Built for the grind. Track the gains. Hit the goal.
